<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361328" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/>Viro Insigni atque <abbr>Doctiss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089586140" type="person">Petrus Antonius
                    Michelotti</rs>.</opener>
<p><lb/>Tibi gratias ago maximas Vir Ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cissime pro iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad me scripsisti
                    <lb/>summa cum humanitate.</p>
<p><lb/>Intelliges ab <abbr>Illustriss.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> Tuo
                    <lb/>causam, propter quam difertur
                    <lb/>solemnis Tua vocatio: quare eam
                    <lb/>hic non repet<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>. Addam sol<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m
                    <lb/>quod solemnis Tua vocatio certissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ma est, brevique sequetur tran<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quillo existente <rs type="organisation">Senatu</rs>, a quo si<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gillum addetur decreto <abbr>Illustr.</abbr> <abbr>D. D.</abbr>
                    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696" type="persons">Moderatorum.</rs> Mihi ante <subst><del>de<gap/></del><add>decem</add></subst>
<pb facs="1361329" n="2"/>
                    <lb/>dies spem<choice><sic> certissam</sic><corr> certissimam</corr></choice> dedit <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <choice><abbr>Pro<unclear>c</unclear>u.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>Procurator</expan></choice> <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1253768439" type="person">Venerius</rs> de Tua solemni vocatione,
                    <lb/>iussitque ut ad Te scriberem<del>,</del>
<lb/>de hac re dicendo illam esse
                    <lb/>vicinam. Statim ac solemnis
                    <lb/>vocatio sequetur Te certiorem
                    <lb/>faciam. Ceterum Tibi respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dendum public<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> non erit,
                    <lb/>sol<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m accept<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vocatione iter
                    <lb/>ad nos suscipies. Etenim ego
                    <lb/>dixi Te esse <abbr>paratiss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr> ad inserviendum
                    <lb/><choice><orig>Huic</orig><reg>huic</reg></choice> <abbr>Sereniss.</abbr> et <abbr>Potentiss.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Rei<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>public<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>.</p>
<p><lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089923198" type="person">Verzale<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>
                    <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_KTF3XKWP">liber</rs> iniuriis plenus
                    <lb/><choice><orig>Contra</orig><reg>contra</reg></choice> Amicissimum nostrum
                    <pb facs="1361330" n="3"/><lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermannum</rs><note type="editorial">Hermann, Jacob (1678-1733)</note> ad manus meas perve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nit, in quo arroganter scribit quod
                    <lb/>si <rs key="pers_DE-588-118537229" type="person">Galileus</rs>, <rs key="pers_DE-588-118872621" type="person">Cavalerius</rs> atque <rs key="pers_DE-588-118659359" type="person">Bo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rellus</rs> <add>in <rs key="place_KON-italie" type="place">Italia</rs></add> non extitissent, non habe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>retis Vos Ultra Montani <rs key="pers_DE-588-100703828" type="person">Walli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sium</rs>, <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtonum</rs>, atque <rs key="pers_DE-588-118571249" type="person">Leib<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nitium</rs>. Hactenus nihil contra
                    <lb/><choice><abbr>Celeber.</abbr><expan>Celeberrimum</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> aut contra
                    <lb/>Te<del> non</del> inveni in illo arrogan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissimo <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_KTF3XKWP">libro</rs>. Tu interim vale, <lb/>Te ad iter
                    dispone, meque ama<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re ne desinas rogo.</p>
<closer><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Vene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. <orig>d</orig><reg>d.</reg></abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1716-07-24">24 Julii 1716</date>.</dateline>
<lb/><abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus</rs> Agnatus Tuus Tibi sa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lutem plurimam mittit.</closer>
